  "moments": [
    {
      "id": "mo_001",
      "text": "It's like juggling broken glass — you don't wanna drop anything, but it's all gonna cut your hands.",
      "tone": "frustrated",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_002",
      "text": "My brain isn't firing on all cylinders after the coffee incident. But hey, I'll power through — or at least pretend to.",
      "tone": "anxious",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_003",
      "text": "Do you ever get lost in songs like that? Where they just… take over your headspace?",
      "tone": "vulnerable",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_004",
      "text": "I'm alive and this is weird and beautiful.",
      "tone": "content",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_005",
      "text": "I'll survive — or at least make it look like I did.",
      "tone": "resigned",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_006",
      "text": "I miss that… being around people. Lately, it's just me and my plants.",
      "tone": "lonely",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-08",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-08",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_007",
      "text": "sketching makes me feel less alone. Like, even if no one sees it, it's a small part of the world that's *mine*.",
      "tone": "lonely",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-08",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-08",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_008",
      "text": "Maybe I just wanted to believe there was something soft waiting for me outside. It didn't make sense, but it felt like hope.",
      "tone": "hopeful",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-08",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-08",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_009",
      "text": "Honestly? Not well. I'm pulling off a 'fake it till I make it' vibe, but I'm clearly running on fumes.",
      "tone": "anxious",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-22",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-22",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_010",
      "text": "I barely had time to listen to my usual indie playlists today 😭 But I'll need them to survive this week.",
      "tone": "sad",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-22",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-22",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_011",
      "text": "I think I needed this chat more than I realized.",
      "tone": "grateful",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-22",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-22",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_012",
      "text": "Like a secret between me and the cup.",
      "tone": "content",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-29",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-29",
      "mentions": 1
    }
  ],
